The slimy monster knocked her down and tied her hands to the slime-puddle below her.\.\.\.

Eeew\..\..\.. gross.\ I can't get out of this thing!

In a swift motion the slime grabbed her shoes and slid it off her feet.
Hey! Those are mine.\. What's the reason for that?
The reason was clear as soon as a few tentacles grew out of the stocks and approached her feet.\|\.
That moment Rarity had a bad feeling about this.\.\. Her confidence diminished and she secretly knew what was about to come.
W\.-\.wait\. a m\.-\.minute! W-\.what are y-\.\.you going to do with these?
Just as she finished her sentence the tentacles hit their target!
Even though she couldn't see it properly, she definitely could feel it. The tentacles started tickling her feet!
With smooth movements the pointy ends of the slimy tickle tools glided around her soles.
Even though the slime was a soft glibbery mass, the tendrills of that monster were still able to tickle with pointy endings.
Rarity tried hard to fight the urge of laughing. However because of the fact that she always treated
her feet perfectly, this was a fight she could not win. Having something tickling her smooth and very
sensitive feet she soon let out her first giggles.
The slime however didn't even bother to stop. Instead more tentacles shot out of the stocks to join the others!
Now both soles were fully toyed with several slimy tendrills, that loved to sroke and dig into her sensitive flesh.
They wiggled between her toes and tickled them. Two nasty tendrills split their endings into more tendrills
to tickle in and around her arches. They harshly dug into that sensitive area driving Rarity wild.
HAHAHAHA!!\. NAHAHA!!\. MAHAHAKE IHIHIT STOHOHOP!!\. PLEAHEHEHESE!!
